r going forward. See descriptions in the individual commits for some of the specifics of the changes and fixes, and how to change existing code to use these API correctly. In followup stages, most code relevant to precompile_utils, trim, and even the allocation-checker should consider being moved into Julia also now, since being written in C/C++ is currently providing negative value for maintaining those, and the change in the API boundary should now make that additional conversion easier.

