Then the process hangs forever. 
I've checked the 1.9.4 tag of Julia, It seems the `crt_sig_handler` in `signals-win.c` is triggered:
```
// line 88 and below
    default: // SIGSEGV, SIGTERM, SIGILL, SIGABRT
